{
  "stem": "17337.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, I mean, you know, they were fabrics on his-- under his name.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they built for the workers these apartments.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then after the war, we stay in this apartment-- beautiful apartments, can't complain.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had, like, a three-bedroom apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we were there together about six or seven-- we were together, girls and, and boys, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was UNRRA at that time, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we got rations from the UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you met people, you know, what, what-- from, from camps where you were and from other camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were a lot people from, from Schindler there in that camp, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in 1946, I met one of the girls what we used to live together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And you-- I had an uncle-- I think I mentioned-- who used to live in Brazil, in Rio de Janeiro.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I, I remember his address by heart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, you know, they used to come every day and-- asking, you want to send a telegram someplace, or whatever?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's nice.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I figured I wasn't sure if that telegram is going to get someplace.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I knew his address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I gave the address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after a few weeks, I got a letter from him that he wants to bring me over to Brazil.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] So and except that, I had-- you know, every day, were coming from different country, from South America, from the United States.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I just-- whenever they came, I register, you know, to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I registered to go to Canada, to South America.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wherever anybody ask me if you want to go someplace, I registered.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
